  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682860/extras/a7dc48815696ef29c7a2cfde08517a15.avif?t=1758961224\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In The Dark Horde, time is your most valuable resource. Every action you take costs Time Units (TUs), forcing you to think ahead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682860/extras/9a9fe474e8f75eede8047863342bfae0.poster.avif?t=1758961224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682860/extras/9a9fe474e8f75eede8047863342bfae0.webm?t=1758961224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682860/extras/9a9fe474e8f75eede8047863342bfae0.mp4?t=1758961224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you've spent your TUs, you must wait for your turn to resume. You can only play cards or abilities when Time is paused, so think strategically!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682860/extras/d1c7bcbbf014ea9e67e9d71d2ba0d921.avif?t=1758961224\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Summon powerful minions and cast devastating spells from your dark spellbook. Experiment with synergies between your cards to unleash devastating combos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682860/extras/dfc928ad510b76ca7332158915e23515.poster.avif?t=1758961224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682860/extras/dfc928ad510b76ca7332158915e23515.webm?t=1758961224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682860/extras/dfc928ad510b76ca7332158915e23515.mp4?t=1758961224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether commanding demons or invoking Death itself, build an army to overwhelm your enemies and dominate the battlefield.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682860/extras/bf2e5b7971d36000fcbda88d025f9ddc.avif?t=1758961224\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The objective is clear: either plunder the enemy Village or survive for 3 days against waves of angry Villagers. Every round starts with 180 Time Units.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682860/extras/b050ceab20259f7a640a3cfc8363f1c8.poster.avif?t=1758961224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682860/extras/b050ceab20259f7a640a3cfc8363f1c8.webm?t=1758961224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682860/extras/b050ceab20259f7a640a3cfc8363f1c8.mp4?t=1758961224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend them wisely to play cards or actions, then wait for your next turn. Seize gold, harvest souls, and destroy the enemy settlement!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682860/extras/edb8a0ec4f814774da89c19e6e08d92c.avif?t=1758961224\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With every victory, earn loot to enhance your deck. Upgrade cards, abilities, and unlock new, powerful skills to strengthen your strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682860/extras/d10adaa894ce80bf915ffd31e47d6433.poster.avif?t=1758961224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682860/extras/d10adaa894ce80bf915ffd31e47d6433.webm?t=1758961224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682860/extras/d10adaa894ce80bf915ffd31e47d6433.mp4?t=1758961224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The choices you make will shape your path—plan carefully, upgrade strategically, and prepare for increasingly challenging encounters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682860/extras/ecb8a8b61134490d74fa816d242976d9.poster.avif?t=1758961224\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682860/extras/ecb8a8b61134490d74fa816d242976d9.webm?t=1758961224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682860/extras/ecb8a8b61134490d74fa816d242976d9.mp4?t=1758961224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features of The Dark Horde:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>20 Starter Decks</strong> – Experiment with 20 unique decks, each offering different strategies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless Mode</strong> – Face limitless challenges for continuous fun.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Permanent Progression</strong> – Unlock stronger starting options as you level up.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Permanent Rewards</strong> – Upgrade a card after each victorious run. Forever.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>200+ Cards</strong>  – Expand your deck from over 200 unique cards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hundreds of Synergies</strong> – Discover powerful combos for devastating strategies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>High Replayability</strong> – Every run offers fresh challenges and strategies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stunning Soundtrack</strong> – Enjoy an immersive soundtrack by Alexander Nakarada.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless Supply of Goblin Looters</strong> – Send goblins to their doom without a second thought... They make funny noises when they die!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682860/extras/677ffcc67fd9bd18b3e7b064e5a3e4bc.poster.avif?t=1758961224\" width=600 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682860/extras/677ffcc67fd9bd18b3e7b064e5a3e4bc.webm?t=1758961224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682860/extras/677ffcc67fd9bd18b3e7b064e5a3e4bc.mp4?t=1758961224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
